SEO note
These pages become your strongest local SEO moat over time.

Section 7: Tools preview

Purpose: utility, trust, backlinks later

Headline
Tools that make decisions clearer

4 tool cards

Mortgage affordability (Montreal)

Rent vs buy (Montreal)

Rental cash flow estimator

Closing costs in Quebec

CTA
